INSTALL

* Requirement
  For running
  1. JRE 1.6 (http://java.sun.com)
  For running & using jsp
  1. JDK 1.6 (http://java.sun.com)
  For building
  1. JDK 1.6 (http://java.sun.com)
  2. ANT 1.7 (http://ant.apache.org)

* Download & running
  For using
  1. Download neurasthenia.tar.gz (http://kldp.net/projects/neurasthenia/download)
  2. Decompress it
  3. cd neurasthenia
  4. ./boot.sh (for unix), boot.bat (for windows)

* For development
  1. Checkout neurasthenia (http://kldp.net/projects/neurasthenia/src)
  2. cd neurasthenia
  3. ant
  4. ./boot.sh (for unix), boot.bat (for windows)
